Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.4.15)
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Homepage: https://github.com/rogerwang/node-webkit

Package: node-webkit
Architecture: i386
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, openssl, zlib1g, libnss3
Description: Call all Node.js modules directly from DOM
 node-webkit is an app runtime based on Chromium and node.js. You can write
 native apps in HTML and Javascript with node-webkit. It also lets you to call
 Node.js modules directly from DOM and enables a new way of writing native
 applications with all Web technologies.
 .
